{"tid":2509504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東涌映灣園菲傭初步確診帶變種病毒","createTime":"2021-04-29T13:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T14:48:03.000Z","uid":212702,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d8d4c35ea139e49bd775809d2667716adf27131a","tid":2509504,"uid":212702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:03:17.000Z","msg":"第11座今日發現一宗感染源頭不明初步確診，初步顯示涉及變種病毒株，經評估後相關區域感染風險有機會較高，政府經檢測呈陽性後決定就相關區域作出限制與檢測宣告。據了解，患者被驗出帶有N501Y變異病毒株，是一名菲傭，如確診將是第四宗社區變種病毒。據悉，今次帶變異病毒株的菲傭，並非近期來港或剛於酒店完成強制檢疫後發現的個案，衞生防中護中心正調查她在港時間及行蹤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676c2418a94158ff87104843f085316ba0933abe","tid":2509504,"uid":377617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:03:40.000Z","msg":"大檸樂了"},{"pid":"613d249be407d83aea45eacc66183ef70683af09","tid":2509504,"uid":92650,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:05:49.000Z","msg":"感謝賓賓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />D賓賓放假成日聚埋一齊,無皇管,遲早送大禮"},{"pid":"4da83f9c3c7dd80a7b8adb835e298362c0c9ee39","tid":2509504,"uid":234553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:07:26.000Z","msg":"成人台食賓賓個班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1bb3c1e09b721fe26a5f9949da3816fc756858","tid":2509504,"uid":212702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:10:32.000Z","msg":"漏水不漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似唔係印度嗰隻超級變種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，下次再努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebd1ecb5200013dbdac63dadfe245949a8709bd","tid":2509504,"uid":9542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"613d249be407d83aea45eacc66183ef70683af09","tid":2509504,"uid":92650,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:05:49.000Z","msg":"感謝賓賓<img src=\